movieareas-api

provide movie api for a reactjs app

# important commands

'npm install'
'npm run server'
'git init'
'git add .'
'git commit -m 'your msg''
git push - u orgin main
git push


http://localhost:6969/movies/getmovies - get all movies
 http://localhost:6969/movies/create - post - Add an movie
 payload sample: {
    "title":"villu",
    "desc": "villu description"
}
 http://localhost:6969/movies/:id - put - update a movie
 http://localhost:6969/movies/:id - delete - delete a movie